    {
      "text": "This was all very clearly, cleanly, economically + simply expressed in that \"clock-timed voice\" dream. {Note} The Lamptons' \"maze\" explanation of Valis is substantially correct - + very Gnostic, although not so labelled.\n\n{Note:} Thus the 2-74 disinhibition can now be seen to have been (1) no accident; + (2) quite obviously self-induced (in the broadest possible sense).\n\nI will conclude this nightmare marathon analysis by noting that my 10 volume meta novel can herewith be newly -+ perhaps final",
      "matched_alias": "Frozen Journey",
      "term_id": "TERM_frozen-journey",
