      "term_slug": "frozen-journey"
    },
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 90 - 190\nG 134\n\ndream opened up (last night like a door). I saw that the ambiance + the milieu, the time + place of the dream (I mean the \"He lived a long time ago...\" etc dream) is the same as the \"lake\" dream. I could see in my mind either Stanton or Lincoln, as if I were still dreaming it: the stove pipe hat, the beard, the type style + format of the newspaper. The mid-19th century USA, the Civil War. This was not a figuring out, a logical reasoning (last night); it was pure un",
